# QuizForge — frontend environment configuration (TEMPLATE)
#
# Vite only exposes env vars prefixed with `VITE_`. Copy this file to
# `frontend/.env.local` (gitignored) to override the API base URL during
# local development — e.g. point at a deployed backend or a non-default
# port. In production on Render, the same variable is set in render.yaml.

# Full base URL of the backend API (no trailing slash, no /api suffix —
# the client appends /api/* itself). Leave empty to use the same-origin
# /api path, which is what the Vite dev proxy expects.
# Example values:
#   VITE_API_URL=                              # local dev (Vite proxy)
#   VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8000         # alternative local setup
#   VITE_API_URL=https://my-app.onrender.com  # deployed backend